<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='701416' id='t-701416'>stuck it in a vase of water,</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='702859' id='t-702859'>it was all right for another two weeks after this.</span>
</span>
</p>
<p class='talk-transcript__para'>
