<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='751474' id='t-751474'>to feed livestock here in Europe.</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='753921' id='t-753921'>At the same time we throw away millions of tons</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='756223' id='t-756223'>of food waste which we could and should be feeding them.</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='759442' id='t-759442'>If we did that, and fed it to pigs, we would save</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='762304' id='t-762304'>that amount of carbon.</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='764655' id='t-764655'>If we feed our food waste which is the current</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='767747' id='t-767747'>government favorite way of getting rid of food waste,</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='770042' id='t-770042'>to anaerobic digestion, which turns food waste</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='772843' id='t-772843'>into gas to produce electricity,</span>
