<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='778880' id='t-778880'>per ton of food waste. It's much better to feed it to pigs.</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='781362' id='t-781362'>We knew that during the war. (Laughter)</span>
</span>
</p>
<p class='talk-transcript__para'>
<data class='talk-transcript__para__time'>
13:15
</data>
<span class='talk-transcript__para__text'>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='784622' id='t-784622'>A silver lining: It has kicked off globally,</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='788896' id='t-788896'>the quest to tackle food waste.</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='790666' id='t-790666'>Feeding the 5,000 is an event I first organized in 2009.</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='794520' id='t-794520'>We fed 5,000 people all on food that otherwise</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='796776' id='t-796776'>would have been wasted.</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='798174' id='t-798174'>Since then, it's happened again in London,</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='800474' id='t-800474'>it's happening internationally, and across the country.</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='802607' id='t-802607'>It's a way of organizations coming together</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='804950' id='t-804950'>to celebrate food, to say the best thing to do with food</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='808692' id='t-808692'>is to eat and enjoy it, and to stop wasting it.</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='811499' id='t-811499'>For the sake of the planet we live on,</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='814092' id='t-814092'>for the sake of our children,</span>
